                <h1>Duke researchers delve into decision making</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/747434d8-6604-46c7-9614-b4e9ae139678.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="" class="w-100">
